**************************************** SSM **************************************************
SSM Service is a free service
Run Command: Execute a document=scripts 
No ssh access to do a run command
SSM Patch manager
     Different patch baseline
          Linux:
               AWS-AmazonLinux2DefaultPatchBaseline
          Windows
               AWS-DefaultPatchBaseline
     Steps to apply patch manager
          1- define a patch baseline to use
          2- define patch group, define based on tags - use tag Patch Group
          3- Define maintenance windows
          4- add the AWS-RunPatchBaseline Run command
          5- Define Rate Control
          6- Monitor Patch Compliance using SSM Inventory
